Class MerchantInfo

java.lang.Object

java.io.Serializable
public class MerchantInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class encapsulates the various merchant specific settings. An instance of this class will be required by most of the other classes in order to properly parameterize the API requests.
